channel.title: What do you use the most?
channel.description:
Well, I got bored and decided too make a topic. Other than java.lang, etc, what do you use the most? For me it is probably java.io, java.net or java.util. Don't be gay and go through the API looking for a really cool, complicated, sophisticated etc class. Just do whatever one comes to mind first.
[19:19] <Budda> if i could post, i would say java.util [19:19] <Budda> or java.awt
